---
import PageLayout from '../../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import Section from '../../components/astro/Section.astro';
---

<PageLayout
  title="Tech Conferences in Zurich | ZurichJS"
  description="Guide to tech conferences in Zurich, Switzerland for JavaScript and web developers."
  keywords={['Tech Conferences Zurich', 'JavaScript Conference Switzerland', 'ZurichJS Conf']}
>
  <Section variant="white" padding="lg">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto animate-fade-in-up">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Tech Conferences in Zurich</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-12">Your guide to developer conferences in Zurich and the Swiss tech ecosystem.</p>

      <div class="space-y-8">
        <div class="bg-js/10 border border-js/20 rounded-xl p-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">ZurichJS Conf 2026</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">The first-ever ZurichJS Conference is coming! A full-day conference dedicated to JavaScript, TypeScript, and modern web development.</p>
          <a href="/waitlist/conf" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 bg-black text-white rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-gray-800 transition-colors">
            Join the Waitlist
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
          <h2>Zurich's Tech Conference Scene</h2>
          <p>Zurich is one of Europe's leading tech hubs, home to ETH Zurich, Google's largest engineering office outside the US, and hundreds of startups.</p>

          <h3>Notable Tech Conferences in Switzerland</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>ZurichJS Conf</strong> - JavaScript and TypeScript (Coming 2026)</li>
            <li><strong>Swiss PGDay</strong> - PostgreSQL community</li>
            <li><strong>DevOpsDays Zurich</strong> - DevOps and SRE</li>
            <li><strong>AI+X Summit</strong> - Artificial Intelligence</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 text-center">
        <a href="/" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Back to Home</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>
</PageLayout>
